y=\sum a_kx^k
xy=\sum a_kx^{k+1}=\sum a_{k-1}x^k
y'=\sum ka_kx^{k-1}=\sum(k+1)a_{k+1}x^k
y''=\sum k(k+1)a_{k+1}x^{k-1}=\sum(k+1)(k+2)a_{k+2}x^k
0=\sum(a_{k-1}+(k+1)a_{k+1}+(k+1)(k+2)a_{k+2})x^k
a_{k-1}+(k+1)a_{k+1}+(k+1)(k+2)a_{k+2}=0
